              </p>
            </li>
<li class="list itemizedlist">
              <p class="para">Veja também o <a href="http://www.redbooks.ibm.com/abstracts/gg243376.html" class="ulink" title="http://www.redbooks.ibm.com/abstracts/gg243376.html">TCP/IP Tutorial and Technical Overview</a> no IBM Redbook.</p>
            </li>
<li class="list itemizedlist">
              <p class="para">Outra fonte é o <a href="http://oreilly.com/catalog/9780596002978/" class="ulink" title="http://oreilly.com/catalog/9780596002978/">TCP/IP Network Administration</a> da O'Reilly.</p>
            </li>
</ul></div></div></div>
